      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 320hp through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant benefits from recent preventative maintenance, including an updated IMS bearing and rear main seal. Handling is sharpened by a factory-spec M030 sport suspension, ensuring neutral turn-in and excellent lateral stability. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management. Finished in Arctic Silver, this chassis remains rigid and communicative, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
