    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Executive Sport Sedan that perfectly balances luxury with reliable performance. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though a detailed walk-around reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, pea-sized indentation on the rear quarter panel\u2014strictly cosmetic and consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium charcoal leather is supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All interior electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the vehicle is mechanically robust. It features a complete service history with recent appointments for a full synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This car has been smoke-free, garage-kept, and is ready for its next owner to drive home with total confidence.",
      "price": 32500.0,
